\is1 Introduction
\ip This the second letter of Apustul John the sabeka of followers of Jesus. Impeendiye din the this letter of woman chosen by God and there also of children din. Ne kema ke group buwa of believers the igpasabut din here. This the malepet letter, mighangyu of it’s necessary eg-ikul of kamalehetan and egpaheyinaweey the tagse sabeka, and migpaney-paney also this concerning the people migpanulu ware kun migpekeetew si Jesus the messiah.
